abstract:
We generalise the fusion procedure for the $A_{
-1}^{(1)}$ open spin chain ($
>2$) and we show that the transfer matrix satisfies a crossing property. We use these results to solve the $A_{
-1}^{(1)}$ open spin chain with $U_{q} (SU(
))$ symmetry by means of the analytical Bethe ansatz method. Our results coincide with the known ones obtained by means of the nested Bethe ansatz.
